OL,3,C'Probable' patient would have survived
OL,4,Cwith different care, coroner says
OL,6,FIt is probable a mental health patient
OL,7,Fin would have survived with different
OL,8,Fcare, a coroner has concluded.
OL,10,FMichael Watkins, 60, died from cardiac
OL,11,Farrest in August 2021 after having a
OL,12,Frare and life-threatening reaction,
OL,13,Fknown as Neuroleptic Malignant
OL,14,FSyndrome (NMS), to antipsychotic drugs
OL,15,Fto treat his schizophrenia.
