OL,3,C'Probable' patient would have survived
OL,4,Cwith different care, coroner says
OL,6,FAlthough the coroner ruled the death
OL,7,Fwas natural causes, she explained that
OL,8,Fnot transferring Mr Watkins from the
OL,9,Fisland's mental health facility
OL,10,FOrchard House to the hospital where he
OL,11,Fcould be given acute care, along with
OL,12,Fa delay in checking test results,
OL,13,Famounted to neglect.
OL,15,FThe inquest heard how Mr Watkins'
OL,16,Fblood results were available on the
OL,17,Fevening of Saturday 14 August and
OL,18,Fwould have shown he was reacting
OL,19,Fnegatively to the drug.
