OL,3,C'Probable' patient would have survived
OL,4,Cwith different care, coroner says
OL,6,FHowever, they were only read on the
OL,7,Fmorning of Monday 16 August, the same
OL,8,Fday he died.
OL,10,FAfter seeing the results, a decision
OL,11,Fwas made at 10.51am for him to be sent
OL,12,Fto the hospital.
OL,14,FHowever, he went into cardiac arrest
OL,15,Fminutes later and died.
