OL,3,C'Probable' patient would have survived
OL,4,Cwith different care, coroner says
OL,6,F"We accepted entirely the findings of
OL,7,Fthe serious incident learning review
OL,8,Fthat was conducted following Mr
OL,9,FWatkins' death, including the
OL,10,Fidentified care and treatment concerns
OL,11,Fwithin both the General Hospital and
OL,12,Fwithin Mental Health Services."
OL,14,FMr Weir added that actions that since
OL,15,FMr Watkins's death, actions have been
OL,16,Ftaken to lower the risk of this
OL,17,Fhappening again.
OL,19,FHe explained: "There is of course
OL,20,Fstill further work to do, and we are
OL,21,Fcommitted to ensuring this happens.
