OL,3,C'Probable' patient would have survived
OL,4,Cwith different care, coroner says
OL,6,F"We would also wish to reassure people
OL,7,Fusing mental health services that
OL,8,FNeuroleptic Malignant Syndrome (NMS)
OL,9,Fis very rare indeed and ask that they
OL,10,Fcontact their mental health
OL,11,Fprofessionals if they have any
OL,12,Fconcerns."
